data.description: Located in the highly desirable Western Ridge subdivision of Ventana Ranch, this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts an impressive array of features.Step inside to discover a spacious layout, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The open-concept living area seamlessly connects to the kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances. The cozy family room features a fireplace - ideal for gathering on chilly evenings. The master suite offers a serene retreat, featuring a lavish ensuite bathroom with a tub and separate shower. Outside, your oasis awaits, complete with a refreshing swimming pool, perfect for summer days. The expansive patio area provides plenty of space for lounging and dining.Located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining, opportunity awaits!
